cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

Class QueryEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine.QueryEngine

  • public class QueryEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    The QueryEngine class supports the execution of Knowledge Graph queries. Queries are provided in N_Triple format which it searches in the knowledges graph and prints results on standard output.
    Author:
    Siddharth Singh
